166
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu je jedno...

167
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeligorski kotar, Lika, Slavonija...

168
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, i sad samo da se vratim na taj kapitalizam.

169
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tu gledam jednu kontradikciju, da ne budem pros,

170
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:18,000
