189
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ljudi se onda polakome.

190
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] I taj jedan mentalitet kapitalistički je duboko ušo u sporu Hrvatskog društva.

191
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, ponavljam, nisu o dva kandidata, ja sam svjesna da su oni toga,

192
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:58,000
