461
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja vjerovatnije moram odmah reći, nećiš na glasovanje,

462
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] ili ja imam nekih drugih obveza, razumijete.

463
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u svom slučaju to nek se ljudi na...

464
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali očuto kaza da je njegova retorika i tu zato moram...

465
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:34,000
