468
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] čak i gospodina Herberta Kikla.

469
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čini mi se da sam ga čak jedan put poznao Kikla,

470
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] imao sam predavanje u Klagenfurtu.

471
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] To vam moja da se malo pohvalim.

472
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I o Njemci svom ja sam duhovni Njemac.

473
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,000
