476
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Seobi stanovništva.

477
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Seobi stanovništva.

478
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] I što sam vam tijel reći?

479
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Premda da se razumemo i desnica u Austrije,

480
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ne pravim digresije.

481
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:12,000
