482
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli ste da je Milanović retorikom vrlo blizak.

483
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je vrlo blizak to uopće.

484
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možda je tu upravo njegova prednost.

485
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ima to jedan ljevičarsku patinu.

486
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mu to daju jednu iznesnu slobodu govora.

487
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što recimo jednom AFD-ovcu iz Njemačke,

488
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je druga najpostrajna stranka po jačini.

489
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:33,000
