491
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo jaka desničarska stranka u Austriji.

492
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili da ne kažem nacionalni zbor u Francijskoj.

493
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Užasno jaka stranka.

494
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni moraju se, pak sad imate tu jednu obrnutu,

495
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se kažem, sam možda pretežak, obrnutu dijalektiku.

496
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se žele dotvoriti Izraelu.

497
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Žele se pokazati kao senitofili, da tako kažem.

498
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo iz te jednog lošeg pedigreja.

499
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Desnice, znate sami da je do jučeri, do prekvičera,

500
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:08,000
