549
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, jedna je stvar govoriti

550
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] o dnevno političkim događajama u Americi,

551
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali stvarno poznavati Ameriku.

552
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] A vi ste tamo živjeli?

553
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nije to, pazite, nije ni to dovoljno.

554
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:53,000
