559
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] može čovjek jako dugo živjeti u Americi

560
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ne shvatiti bit Amerike.

561
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:11,000
