615
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da ne odemo sad po Hrvatska vesnica.

616
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne idemo predaleko.

617
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Glamno Trump, zašto je on bitan?

618
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bitan je toliko što on ima jednu svoju.

619
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] On nije političar. On nije agit propovac.

620
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on odskače od svih dosadačnih, apsolutno od svih.

621
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Od Jeffersona pa do Woodrow Wilsona pa do Busha pa do Obama i do zadnjeg Bidena.

622
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odskače upravo zbog toga što on je neovisan.

623
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] On ne ovisi o lobijima.

624
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Premda, on mora logično voditi računa i o lobijima.

625
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:25,000
